{"tid":488671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史突破！全球第一批智能巴士深圳首發","createTime":"2017-12-04T02:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T05:41:14.000Z","uid":20058,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d657589e54a5551b9cd7ecd65043005be404fdf9","tid":488671,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"4台阿爾法巴智能駕駛公交今日（2日）上午在深圳舉行首發儀式，這是全球首次在開放道路上進行智能駕駛公交試運行，標誌著智能駕駛公交已具備上路條件。<br />\n<br />\n這批智能公交車滿載25人。車輛運行時速25公里，最高時速40公里。單次續航里程可達150公里。<br />\n<br />\n「阿爾法巴智能駕駛公交系統」以國產、自主可控的智能駕駛技術為基礎，具備包括激光雷達、毫米波雷達、攝像頭、GPS天線等感知設備在內的7道安全防線，能夠對其他道路使用者和突發狀況做出實時反應，可實現自動駕駛下的行人、車輛檢測，減速避讓、緊急停車、障礙物繞行、變道、自動按站停靠等功能。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://v.wenweipo.com/video/17422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.wenweipo.com%2Fvideo%2F17422&d=ZZPNaLy14umPRrz0OKTL23Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=062e776e\" target=\"_blank\">http://v.wenweipo.com/video/17422</a><br />\n人地法國已經玩緊無人巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a426d2fb7b1262d153fe23847ee5d61a32d66e","tid":488671,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地法國已經玩緊無人巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那人命唔值錢"},{"pid":"59bc2832ed20ba535e20cba37d06be3ddbca3bc4","tid":488671,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"無人巴士5天測試無意外　<br />\n台北市宣布將擴大實施<br />\n<br />\n2017/08/05<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20170805/1175983/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20170805%2F1175983%2F&d=ZZPNaLy14umPRrz0OKTL23Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b68fdd1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20170805%2F1175983%2F&h=6d955a41\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20170805/1175983/</a>"},{"pid":"8f0f93c717a6054b9bd4d92